Hi Trevor,



If you&#39;re interested in a java version of NEAT I have attempted to create a
version that is an add-on to the Neuroph neural network framework
(http://sourceforge.net/projects/neuroph/). It is currently unreleased,
however I believe it to be feature complete.



If you&#39;re interested in being a beta tester for this functionality let me
know and I will try to get an archive to the code on the Neuroph site. It
will become a fully supported Neuroph add-on with the next major release.



Cheers,



Aidan



From: neat@yahoogroups.com [mailto:neat@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of Trevor
Burton
